	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.57]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Flowing Thought items are almost essential for bards since we get Meditation capped at 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Other focus items do not affect bard songs at all so don't worry about them.  However, we do get instruments that affect our songs based on category (singing, percussion, string, wind, brass).  These instruments affect bard songs like focus items affect caster spells.  www.EQDiva.com has a spreadsheet that lists the instruments and their affects. You can find it in the Discussions section under the Verses of Victory forum.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
