	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another good money maker is spiderling silk and hides for tailoring.&nbsp;&nbsp;There are a couple of very good farming spots for silks and hides.  Load your bags, sell off everything but LQ, MQ, HQ hides and silks and park yourself in bazaar over night.  No need to get greedy, price your stuff at your server's market standard and it will sell.  Since the advent of Acrylia armor there is alyways a market for LQ hides and spiderling silks.<br><br>Where to camp for silks?  I leave that as an excercise for the young bard :wink<br><br><br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Feb 19 21:30:46 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://calthine.tripod.com target=_new>Calthine Faeriesong</a><br>52 Minstrel of <a href=HTTP://www.tortureguild.org target=_new>Torture</a><br>Vazelle</td></tr>
